{"tid":28873,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓罐頭資料庫","createTime":"2016-12-08T08:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T04:06:20.000Z","uid":21654,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"225b11e0afe6c517d56b9ecedbb6e05616e2899a","tid":28873,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"最近開始餵主人食罐所以研究左好多貓罐頭<br />\n整左個資料庫開心SHARE<br />\n <br />\nTITLE係跟牌子名順序排，包括主／副食罐<br />\n主食罐範指符合AAFCO（美國）／FEDIAF（歐洲）建議嘅營養標準，可當正餐食用，副食罐只可以當小食<br />\n（CANAGAN特例，官網同FAQs都無寫明符合咩營養建議，請自行決定）<br />\n <br />\n碳水化合物同灰質過高會用紅字表示<br />\n備註列左啲需要注意嘅成分, 參考用<br />\n <br />\n有興趣想知有無主子食評SHARE番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17GY16jwgLQUcDsSEG4C5unNUgerd1smD1oquaIpIwvs/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F17GY16jwgLQUcDsSEG4C5unNUgerd1smD1oquaIpIwvs%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=XBtCiekKnBD61yqLsWuThGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=4f8d6a5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17GY16jwgLQUcDsSEG4C5unNUgerd1smD1oquaIpIwvs/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"911ce772ee30fa5d17216cc901b55a66ac0696d1","tid":28873,"uid":51726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd8d3cfe312b1091b4d0392794dc751c6ac4150","tid":28873,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"aba50f63ce3b6639290630592888dde5dcfb8b5a","tid":28873,"uid":59160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"之前餵開kakato（某啲味好咸<br />\n主子鍾意食<br />\n依家轉左weruva（勁淡味<br />\n主子唔鍾意食，食兩啖就走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aca1b84dabfbe70527869e98393a95608d2772","tid":28873,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"食開fussie cat<br />\n我自己試過覺得淡味先係咁買畀佢食<br />\n係咪同人一樣 食太鹹都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aefd92e7edf71ae9149f80a74172a8f4413b10","tid":28873,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"另外巴打 我有好多隻唔同味嘅fussie cat<br />\n有黑鑽同金鑽（類似咁嘅系列）嘅唔同味道<br />\n如果想幫你補啲資料落去可以點畀你？<br />\n但我呢幾日都比較忙 要下星期二後先可以畀到啲資料你<br />\n唔知你介唔介意等咁耐 唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a619f772881777d5509bf655aa83a5b5c3bd3b16","tid":28873,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:40:09.000Z","msg":"有冇D平既罐頭介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企隻喵長期食乾糧,好似唔太健康咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9ee3fbd8539a5e04203a4b07a959e3b7252d13","tid":28873,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇D平既罐頭介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企隻喵長期食乾糧,好似唔太健康咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我通常一次過訂一大堆<br />\n因為多過某個數有折"},{"pid":"6810f4788260bfacb78d5c2e7baee434db622772","tid":28873,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"嘩,巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63eddd3288888ba9793ef18566b33c2b313091a6","tid":28873,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"卡拉膠(炎症/胃腸道癌症)<br />\n係指對抗定會導致?"},{"pid":"d40a1932157f76482dd7b20639d302fefef9a551","tid":28873,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"個衰野食左兩個月kakato<br />\n諗住買d主食罐比佢試下<br />\n點知肉粒同爛肉佢都唔鍾意<br />\n最後廢事哂野就一半半咁撈比佢食先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77b157b91a6473e01474518e89a50a99495ab1e","tid":28873,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇D平既罐頭介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企隻喵長期食乾糧,好似唔太健康咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食乾糧唔係唔健康 而係佢會飲唔夠水<br />\n一日一罐加d水就已經夠一日所需既水一大部分<br />\n睇書話吞拿魚唔係咁健康你可以試下其他魚或者雞<br />\n齋食乾糧而佢又唔鍾意飲水既好容易有腎病<br />\n<br />\n副食罐d人通常推介kakato同applaws<br />\n主食罐就選擇唔多同埋都唔平"},{"pid":"96db3da9a38f6d250320660d2ef22ff25ce9eb17","tid":28873,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T21:40:04.000Z","msg":"可以買一塊雞扒10蚊左右,切一舊出黎水煮睇下隻喵食唔食<br />\n有D人間唔中買D魚比貓食(生又有.水煮又有)<br />\n我自己既結論係可以咩都試下<br />\n魚乾,魷魚絲,麵包,薯片都有比隻貓食過<br />\n<br />\n當然我比隻貓既主食係乾糧同水.其他會當係零食咁樣包括罐頭"},{"pid":"b4dd00a812caf04ab98721ee3d40a95fe4b61ba0","tid":28873,"uid":21654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外巴打 我有好多隻唔同味嘅fussie cat<br />\n有黑鑽同金鑽（類似咁嘅系列）嘅唔同味道<br />\n如果想幫你補啲資料落去可以點畀你？<br />\n但我呢幾日都比較忙 要下星期二後先可以畀到啲資料你<br />\n唔知你介唔介意等咁耐 唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我大部分都喺官網揾，產地就麻煩啲要search<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而我唔建議再食，因為有人造維他命K3 menadione，所以我無再睇佢其他款<br />\n<br />\n好多資料都提到呢樣對貓好差唔應該食<br />\n我無意中睇到外國有貓奴餵左weruva 俾隻貓8個幾月<br />\n(Weruva 同fussie 一樣有menadione)<br />\n(Natural balance 3文魚，nature recipe 都有)<br />\n最後佢隻貓走左，點解走詳細唔太記得但同menadione 中毒有關<br />\n<br />\n天然維他命k喺綠葉植物同肝臟可提取<br />\nMenadione 係用嚟代替佢，令貓罐符合營養標準，食過多會中毒"},{"pid":"d382046a3d94db61e10791c4be60adf04882a954","tid":28873,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個衰野食左兩個月kakato<br />\n諗住買d主食罐比佢試下<br />\n點知肉粒同爛肉佢都唔鍾意<br />\n最後廢事哂野就一半半咁撈比佢食先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁應該鐘意食肉絲?因為KAKATO係肉絲多<br />\n我而家餵緊thrive都係肉絲<br />\n兩隻貓食到唔肯停"},{"pid":"841ae0f696c6fd57de1c82afca519fe2757ba124","tid":28873,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卡拉膠(炎症/胃腸道癌症)<br />\n係指對抗定會導致?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry無寫清楚係導致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰啲乜乜膠作用都係整傑啲汁(唔知點解要咁做)<br />\n呢啲化學嘢少食好啲，如果貓腸胃好勁嘅可能唔怕<br />\n始終隻隻貓接受嘅都唔同<br />\n<br />\n有啲牌子會用薯粉代替<br />\n同膠比會好啲"},{"pid":"67055bcd01441b5595a3f05b56bdf02dc447a1f8","tid":28873,"uid":5011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"諗住訂canagan 罐比主人食，之前買左三罐比佢地試，佢地好鍾意，有無人知成分算唔算好"},{"pid":"7e2503decd8e9457f521284dad77e96ad234fef6","tid":28873,"uid":5011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇完樓主個表 好似全部罐都唔健康咁"},{"pid":"fe91de823271443c899c66e9deacaf39cfd90802","tid":28873,"uid":32716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"灰質有咩害處？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1729650acb06410a4b64c25c48c497c3706c3c10","tid":28873,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇完樓主個表 好似全部罐都唔健康咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無一樣罐係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係除左有人造維他命K3唔建議食<br />\n其他係有啲有膠有啲有薯粉有啲乜都唔落<br />\n睇你選擇<br />\n唔鼓勵食死一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea51474563f3afd9d76a6d32f42801c60773834","tid":28873,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5496544e6653f4c91b116e70df5b7e4516bea10a","tid":28873,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>灰質有咩害處？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔算係唔好，只係標示可以吸收幾多營養<br />\n灰質係指扣除左蛋白質、脂肪、纖維、碳水化合物剩底嘅嘢<br />\n礦物質同無用嘅碳化物都歸呢類<br />\n理論係灰質多無用嘅嘢就多左，相對需要嘅營養就少左<br />\n本身唔會影響健康"},{"pid":"4111e036f9fd880b59c0a5c88365201069225b37","tid":28873,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住訂canagan 罐比主人食，之前買左三罐比佢地試，佢地好鍾意，有無人知成分算唔算好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCanagan成份無問題，無膠<br />\n用木薯粉代替整傑啲汁<br />\n只係我揾唔到佢跟咩營養標準<br />\n不過佢聲稱係complete food<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74330b9cd53f48d27fe9e94a145f2643c7a5e604","tid":28873,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個衰野食左兩個月kakato<br />\n諗住買d主食罐比佢試下<br />\n點知肉粒同爛肉佢都唔鍾意<br />\n最後廢事哂野就一半半咁撈比佢食先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁應該鐘意食肉絲?因為KAKATO係肉絲多<br />\n我而家餵緊thrive都係肉絲<br />\n兩隻貓食到唔肯停</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwow 試試佢先 thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f743dda5cc84e2301cd722b30cd83573e8b529","tid":28873,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:36:58.000Z","msg":"會唔會整啲白烚雞肉畀佢好過食罐頭？"}]}